DROP TABLE [dbo].[Student]
GO

SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO

CREATE TABLE [dbo].[Student]
( 
	[Name1] [varchar](50)  NULL,
	[Name2] [varchar](50)  NULL,
	[Maths1] [int]  NULL,
	[Maths2] [int]  NULL,
	[Science1] [int]  NULL,
	[Science2] [int]  NULL,
	[English1] [int]  NULL,
	[English2] [int]  NULL
)
WITH
(
	DISTRIBUTION = ROUND_ROBIN,
	CLUSTERED COLUMNSTORE INDEX
)
GO
